# CLAUDE.md

This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.

## Project Overview

A single-file bilingual (Chinese/English) interactive quiz webpage — "AI时代核心知识综合测试 / Comprehensive Core Knowledge Quiz in the AI Era". Contains 43 questions testing knowledge about LLMs, AI companies, AI concepts, and industry trends.

## File Structure

- `ytb.html` — The entire application: HTML structure, CSS styling, quiz data (`qData` array), and JavaScript logic (selection, scoring, reset, TXT export of wrong answers).

## How to use

Open `ytb.html` in any browser. No build step, no dependencies, no server required.

## Quiz Data Format

Each question object in `qData`:
```js
{
    qZ: "Chinese question text",
    qE: "English question text",
    oZ: ["4 Chinese options"],
    oE: ["4 English options"],
    a: 0,          // index of correct answer (0-based)
    eZ: "Chinese explanation",
    eE: "English explanation"
}
```

When adding questions, append to the `qData` array. Keep both languages in sync — each index in `oZ` must correspond to the same index in `oE`.
